  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When you choose this Creed at 3rd level, select one nature release. (Earth, Wind, Fire, Water, or Lightning Release). If you select a nature release you already have, you can instead learn one jutsu of the chosen nature release that you qualify for. You are now able to add jutsu with the corresponding keyword to your jutsu list.</p><p>Additionally, you gain proficiency in Ninshou and Chakra Control and ability checks using either of these skills using Constitution or Intelligence.</p><p>Finally, you have learned to augment even the most basic strikes into explosive displays of power. When you deal damage to a creature with <em><strong>Lethal Attack</strong></em> you can change the damage type to your nature release's corresponding damage type. (Water Release = Cold). This damage ignores resistance.</p><p>Starting at 10th level, damage dealt this feature treats immunity as resistance. (These do not stack.)</p><img src=\"systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Cheat%20Sheet/T7%20Natural%20End.png\" />",
